From: patch-rebuild <patches@local>
Subject: [PATCH] topic5: portal LINEAR DmaBuf + CUDA import (no mmap)

Negotiate DmaBuf when SPA omits modifiers. Encode via cuImportExternalMemory
on FFmpeg CUDA context + pitch2D + RGBA_to_NV12. No mmap fallback.

If import fails on a driver/producer, disable enablePortalDmabufLinear (SHM).

